sequenceDiagram
    participant Alice
    participant Bob
    participant Carol

    Alice->>Bob: Hello Bob!
    Bob->>Carol: Forward to Carol
    Carol-->>Alice: Response

    Note over Alice,Carol: Async communication

    alt Successful case
        Alice->>Bob: Request
        Bob-->>Alice: Success
    else Failure case
        Alice->>Bob: Request
        Bob-->>Alice: Error
    end

    loop Every minute
        Alice->>Bob: Ping
        Bob-->>Alice: Pong
    end
